response.original_title: Ms. CEO’s Baby Daddy Is The Merchant of Death
response.overview: Connor Reed was the most untouchable and feared man in the underground world. He was a powerful arms dealer who owned the multi-billion-dollar company called Dominion Tech. But because his life was in danger, he had to know who the real enemy was. So, he had to go on an undercover mission and pretended to be a truck driver.
response.title: Ms. CEO’s Baby Daddy Is The Merchant of Death
